{"tid":611932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥伸出友誼之手 笑稱：賓迪基好撚扭得！！","createTime":"2018-03-31T13:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T18:48:20.000Z","uid":119778,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f89acfd5a434f3d40b90fe1400767c705bb096c4","tid":611932,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/212408_cfe7723e47e3e89494ca34b24301ba2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F212408_cfe7723e47e3e89494ca34b24301ba2e.png&h=178cf3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港球隊雖然無緣競逐今屆英超亞洲盃，未能與英超球員交手，但香港有網絡紅人「爆機達」，周四於《FIFA 18》英超亞洲盃與李斯特城、水晶宮球員過招。 <br />\n<br />\n出席活動的李斯特城球員有尼迪迪、施利文尼、馬列斯及艾馬迪；水晶宮則派出賓迪基、安祖斯唐辛、巴卡利沙高及韋費特沙夏迎戰。他們分成8隊，每位球員跟一位電競高手組隊。 <br />\n<br />\n「達哥」伙拍水晶宮的賓迪基出戰，首場內訌對另一水兵安祖斯唐辛，賓迪基球場上犀利，打機亦有板有眼，為隊伍先開紀錄，「<span style=\"color: red;\">達哥」更倣效賓迪基的入球慶祝動作，場面搞笑。</span> <br />\n<br />\n有主場之利的「達哥」，使出撒手鐧，帶領二人殺入決賽，雖最終得亞軍，<span style=\"color: red;\">但「達哥」稱與賓迪基合作愉快：「賓迪基果然係一線球星，好扭得！」</span>更笑言在球場上未必能扭得贏對手。"},{"pid":"4eedde3ac01c2349316502dfbc0daa1c23dbb680","tid":611932,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"達狗又扮識波"},{"pid":"459afbbce9788dddd206a4fbf4b1225e9051c06b","tid":611932,"uid":119778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4eedde3ac01c2349316502dfbc0daa1c23dbb680","tid":611932,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"達狗又扮識波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"[url]咁樣衰都做到ptgf? <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611785/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611785/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]"},{"pid":"28f76f5ec6055b8f04ec5c9db8f64205ce3a4680","tid":611932,"uid":106701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"459afbbce9788dddd206a4fbf4b1225e9051c06b","tid":611932,"uid":119778,"like